No. 551. Board of County Commissioners of the County of Kearny, Kan., Petitioner, v. Louise M. Irvine; and No. 552. Board of County Commissioners of the County of Kearny, Kan., Petitioner, v. William Edward Coffin et al. January 25, 1904. Mr. Milton Brown, Mr. George Getty and Mr. ■ Chester I. Long for petitioners.

Petitions for writs- of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Eighth ■Circuit denied.

No appearance for respondents.
